[Course_Description]
Discover how to facilitate your creative communication with the aid of the top social media platforms. In this course, Von Glitschka breaks down how to use key features on Instagram, Facebook, LinkedIn, and other platforms to showcase your work, share your creative workflow, and generally grow your online presence. He talks about writing engaging posts on LinkedIn and reviewing audience insights to assess a post's performance. Plus, learn how to write posts to extend your reach on Facebook, find and engage with potential clients on Twitter, use geo-tagging and video on Instagram, and share your work on Behance. This course provides you with a solid introduction to these key platforms so that you can start building a social strategy designed to increase your brand awareness, and help you build a larger client base.